author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how Ubisoft once again digs it's heels in the sand and fights against the ownership of it's games. Stop Killing Games has been one of the most important initiatives and currently the only plan to prevent greedy publishers from restricting access to the games we love. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Ubisoft Absolutely Deserves Their Failure...
